Feature: Test match used in pipe

  Background:
    Given a graph with space named "nba"

  Scenario: Order by after match
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH (n:player{name:"Tim Duncan"})-[]-(m) RETURN n,m | ORDER BY $-.m;
      """
